@node "INFO" "SN AutoUL v1.1 - Information"
@toc "MAIN"
┌──────────────────────────────┐
  SN AutoUL v1.1 - Information
└──────────────────────────────┘

   This makes listing users a little simpler for some users.  Sometimes
they want a list of all users or all users of a certain level and this
makes doing so MUCH easier.

Features to note:
  - Normal and ANSI menus for both kinds of users!
  - Provides the user the option to see a full user listing, by level
    (if they have the access) and by selected parameters.

───SN/AHI (910) 326-3804 (28.8k)─────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
